{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","nameNarration":"","narration":"*Rustle*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"...Is this...what you'd call imposing...?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"There are so many soldiers gathered."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001},{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Is the march to Reims ready?"},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"There's also talk about reinforcing the defense of@Orleans."},{"chara":[{"id":830300}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"The same Orleans that was once reclaimed by the@rumored La Pucelle..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I wish I could fight alongside that miraculous@maiden too!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830300,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Huh...Orleans? La Pucelle?"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"I remember that Miss Jeanne liberated Orleans,@I think..."},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"In 1429! That's before I was born."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"They sounded like they were talking about@a story from just the other day, though..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"This is a world inside someone's mind..."},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"The last book's owner might still be from that time."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Ah..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303},{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801100,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"???","textCenter":"...@..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":801100,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"lipSynch":0,"motion":101,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"[se:7222_happy]...!"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"That person...!"},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"???","textRight":"I am..."},{"chara":[{"id":801100,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"???","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameRight":"???","textRight":"...Who am I?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Huh... You've lost your memories?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Can't you remember anything?"},{"nameRight":"???","textRight":"...I don't know..."},{"nameRight":"???","textRight":"I just...couldn't forgive my father."},{"nameRight":"???","textRight":"If I were king...I would never have let that@person...end up like that!"},{"nameRight":"???","textRight":"I just...kept thinking like that..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":831303,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome & Torte","textCenter":"..."},{"nameCenter":"Perenelle's Voice","textCenter":"That person is Dauphin Louis."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001},{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"It seems like he has lost his memories and is@dreaming of the past."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Father, Mother..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"What happened to Miss Melissa and Miss Elisa?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"You don't need to worry about them."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"Once they drove back Isabeau and her forces,@they were able to return to the Ark of Feelings."},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"After they send King Charles back to his original@world,"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"they'll head this way."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"...This place looks like Roche Castle again."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"It seems like this is from more than ten years@ago...around when Orleans was liberated."},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Upon hearing the rumors of the maiden of miracles,"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"soldiers started gathering from all over."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"That's why it's so noisy..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402901},{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Dauphin Louis","textCenter":"Roche Castle..."},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameCenter":"Dauphin Louis","textCenter":"I must head to the grand hall of the castle..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"slideOutRightFast","id":801100}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Let's follow him!"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Yes."},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I'll make you all invisible so as not to look@suspicious..."},{"autoTurnLast":3.0,"flashEffect":"flashWhiteSlow2","textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_31094.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story13","chara":[{"id":801100,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Dauphin Louis","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":801100}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.ex